benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: POST /1.0/kb/invoiceItems/{invoiceItemId}/customFields - Add custom fields to invoice item

covered: Valid Payload: Scenarios cover successful creation of custom fields with valid payloads.
Invalid Payload: Multiple scenarios test for malformed or missing fields, ensuring proper error handling.
Duplicate Submission: Scenarios address potential issues with duplicate custom field names.
Server Error Handling: Scenarios simulate system errors and validate responses for service unavailability.
gaps: Large Payloads: No tests specifically address handling of very large payloads.
Validation: While some validation scenarios exist, edge cases for field lengths and special characters could be expanded.
Concurrency Issues: No tests cover race conditions when multiple clients attempt to add custom fields concurrently.
recommendations: Add tests for large payloads to ensure the system handles maximum limits appropriately.
Expand validation scenarios to include edge cases for field lengths and special characters.
Include scenarios to test for concurrency issues when multiple requests are made to the same resource.
